form(#twitterSettingsForm="", (submit)="save()")
  mat-card
    mat-card-header
      mat-card-title Twitter Integration
      mat-card-subtitle(*ngIf="!_twitterSettingsClient._IntegrationEnabled")
        | Twitter integration is disabled, run Biliomi in install or update mode to set it up via the installation process.

    mat-card-content(*ngIf="_twitterSettingsClient._IntegrationEnabled")
      chip-list-input([(chips)]="trackedWords", placeholder="Tracked Words")
        | When tracked words are set Biliomi will automagically track the given words on Twitter.
        | Do mind that Twitter limits how much tweets are handled, so use unique words.

      .mat-button-row.mat-button-row-blocks
        edit-template-button(templateKey="TwitterStatusUpdate") Edit Twitter Status Update Template
        edit-template-button(templateKey="TwitterTweetFound") Edit Twitter Tweet Found Template

    mat-card-actions(*ngIf="_twitterSettingsClient._IntegrationEnabled")
      save-button([stateEmitter]="_twitterSettingsClient.afterSave")
      button(mat-button, type="button", (click)="initFields()", matTooltip="Refresh data")
        mat-icon refresh